{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a9dccb343e","title":"给刘松林的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c9c4dfa622","index":0,"year":1956,"month":2,"day":14,"articleId":"a9dccb343e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"635a7fde23","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a9dccb343e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘松林，原名刘思齐，1949年10月同毛泽东之子毛岸英结婚。1950年11月毛岸英在抗美援朝战争中晒性。1955年9月至1957年9月，刘松林在苏联莫斯科大学数学力学系读书。"},{"id":"0c1fb8c987","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a9dccb343e","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"得胜，即李得胜，是毛泽东在陕北时使用过的名字。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3ed9d77632","type":"title","text":"给刘松林\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a9dccb343e"},{"id":"635a7fde23","type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的思齐儿：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a9dccb343e"},{"id":"0c1fb8c987","type":"paragraph","text":"给我的信都收到了，很高兴。希望你注意身体，不使生病，好好学习。我们都好，勿以为念。国内社会主义高涨，你那里有国内报纸否？应当找到报纸，看些国内消息，不要和国内情况太隔绝了","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a9dccb343e"},{"id":"448d7bdea8","type":"paragraph","text":"祝好！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a9dccb343e"},{"id":"7129c88554","type":"subtitle","text":"得胜","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a9dccb343e"},{"id":"26ae1948cf","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年二月十四日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a9dccb343e"}],"page":{"id":"6342629f9d","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a9dccb343e","start":218,"end":218}}}},"__N_SSG":true}